</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">         G                       F#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">      together with the ancient fathers.
                                   
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.    May the light of your Passover,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">      the pledge of love and peace,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">      shine upon your Church.
                                   
